headline: Energy earnings, Fed commentary, inflation data: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime host Josh Lipton previews several of the biggest stories to come on Friday, Jan. 30, including earnings results from companies like SoFi Technologies (SOFI), Exxon Mobil (XOM), Chevron (CVX), and American Express (AXP); commentary from Federal Reserve officials; and fresh inflation data in the form of December's Producer Price Index (PPI).To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime.

headline: Ameriprise Financial’s (NYSE:AMP) Q4 CY2025: Strong Sales
summary: Financial services company Ameriprise Financial (NYSE:AMP) reported revenue ahead of Wall Streets expectations in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 11.1% year on year to $4.96 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $10.83 per share was 5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
